137
00:10:35,176 --> 00:10:36,177
Ah, seu...

138
00:10:37,178 --> 00:10:39,347
Akira, venha comigo agora.

139
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:40,974
Akira, quem é esse cara?

140
00:10:41,057 --> 00:10:45,186
